FROM ME WHILE I WAS ASLEEP?

78
00:08:05,250 --> 00:08:08,083
- I THOUGHT
THAT YOU LOOKED COLD.

79
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:25,083
- FIX MY HAIR.

80
00:08:25,166 --> 00:08:27,916
YOU AT LEAST KNOW HOW
TO DO THAT, DON'T YOU?

81
00:08:32,583 --> 00:08:33,958
WELL, ARE YOU DEAF?

82
00:08:34,041 --> 00:08:36,250
- NOT NOW.
I'M TRYING TO READ.

83
00:08:36,333 --> 00:08:38,000
- ( grumbles )

84
00:08:38,083 --> 00:08:41,000
WHAT IS YOUR PROBLEM?

85
00:08:42,166 --> 00:08:44,583
- FINE, YOU DO IT.
- HUH?

86
00:08:44,666 --> 00:08:47,416
- HELP FIX MY HAIR.

87
00:08:49,666 --> 00:08:51,875
- I DON'T--
- JUST DO IT.

88
00:08:51,958 --> 00:08:54,291
I JUST WISH
IGGY WERE STILL HERE.

89
00:08:54,375 --> 00:08:56,791
- NO MATTER WHO THEY ARE,

90
00:08:56,875 --> 00:08:59,333
THE MASTER IS THE MASTER.

91
00:08:59,416 --> 00:09:02,166
ENTOURAGES CAN'T LIVE
WITHOUT A MASTER.

92
00:09:02,250 --> 00:09:05,791
