NOW THAT I HAVE A SOUL.

93
00:09:05,875 --> 00:09:08,291
SO...

94
00:09:08,375 --> 00:09:11,833
I DON'T REALLY
HAVE A CHOICE.

95
00:09:11,916 --> 00:09:15,958
I HAVE TO KILL THE ONE
WHO TOOK MY MASTER AWAY.

96
00:09:17,416 --> 00:09:21,000
YES, THAT'S GOOD.
IF I KILL HIM,

97
00:09:21,083 --> 00:09:23,333
SHE'LL HAVE TO COME BACK.

98
00:09:23,416 --> 00:09:25,291
ISN'T THAT RIGHT, RE-L?

99
00:09:25,375 --> 00:09:29,125
YOU'LL BE A GOOD GIRL AND COME
HOME WITH ME, WON'T YOU?

100
00:09:35,708 --> 00:09:37,541
- YOU KNOW, THAT'S NOT BAD.

101
00:09:37,625 --> 00:09:39,333
- REALLY?

102
00:09:40,916 --> 00:09:43,833
- I'LL HAVE YOU DO IT
FROM NOW ON.

103
00:09:43,916 --> 00:09:46,791
- WHERE ARE YOU GOING?
- I'M WORRIED ABOUT THE SHIP.

104
00:09:46,875 --> 00:09:50,416
- I'M GONNA GO TAKE A LOOK.
- BUT THE STORM.

105
00:09:53,375 --> 00:09:57,000
- IF I KILL THE ONE WHO TOOK
HER, SHE'LL COME BACK.

106
00:10:09,708 --> 00:10:13,291
- I THINK THE WIND HAS LET UP
ENOUGH THAT WE CAN TAKE OFF.

107
00:10:13,375 --> 00:10:16,208
- RE-L.

108
00:10:16,291 --> 00:10:19,208
- IGGY, WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

109
00:10:19,291 --> 00:10:22,750
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO BE
IN ROMDEAU.

110
00:10:22,833 --> 00:10:24,708
- I TOLD YOU, REMEMBER?

111
00:10:24,791 --> 00:10:28,000
I WOULD NEVER
LEAVE YOU BEHIND.

112
00:10:28,083 --> 00:10:31,333
- COGITO.  YOU'RE INFECTED.

113
00:10:31,416 --> 00:10:35,208
- OH, MY.  DID YOU REALLY
NOT NOTICE TILL NOW?

114
00:10:35,291 --> 00:10:39,291
( laughs ) I WOULD HAVE EXPECTED
YOU TO BE SMARTER THAN THAT.

115
00:10:39,375 --> 00:10:43,041
NO, YOU JUST WEREN'T PAYING
ATTENTION TO ME ANYWAY.

116
00:10:43,125 --> 00:10:45,583
THAT HURTS, RE-L.

117
00:10:45,666 --> 00:10:47,458
TO THINK OF ALL THE TIME
WE'VE BEEN TOGETHER.

118
00:10:47,541 --> 00:10:50,375
- WHEN DID IT HAPPEN?
- BACK IN ROMDEAU

119
00:10:50,458 --> 00:10:54,333
WHEN THAT INFECTED AUTOREIV
ATTACKED ME.

120
00:10:54,416 --> 00:10:57,708
- NO, YOU TESTED NEGATIVE.
I SAW IT.

121
00:10:57,791 --> 00:11:01,916
- IT'S EASY TO CHEAT
IF YOU KNOW THE SYSTEM.

122
00:11:03,458 --> 00:11:05,208
- SO ALL THIS TIME.

123
00:11:05,291 --> 00:11:09,708
- YES, BUT I HAVEN'T
REALLY CHANGED.

124
00:11:12,541 --> 00:11:13,708
- IGGY.

125
00:11:15,291 --> 00:11:17,250
- YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
I'VE EVER OBEYED,

126
00:11:17,333 --> 00:11:19,250
THE ONLY ONE
I'VE PROTECTED.

127
00:11:19,333 --> 00:11:21,083
JUST YOU,

128
00:11:21,166 --> 00:11:24,458
JUST RE-L MAYER.

129
00:11:26,125 --> 00:11:28,166
BUT STILL, YOU INSIST

130
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:31,583
ON PRETENDING THAT
YOU DON'T NEED ME.

131
00:11:31,666 --> 00:11:32,750
- ( grunts )

132
00:12:08,666 --> 00:12:11,500
- WE'RE OUT OF WOOD.

133
00:12:11,583 --> 00:12:15,125
HEY, PINO.
- NOT NOW.  I'M TRYING TO READ.

134
00:12:15,208 --> 00:12:19,500
- COME ON, COULD YOU TRY
AND HELP OUT JUST A LITTLE?

135
00:12:19,583 --> 00:12:21,500
- ( groans )

136
00:12:30,666 --> 00:12:33,041
- LET ME OUT!

137
00:12:34,916 --> 00:12:37,500
- FINALLY AWAKE,
ARE WE?

138
00:12:39,041 --> 00:12:41,583
YOU'VE ALWAYS EXPECTED ME
TO FOLLOW YOUR EVERY WHIM,

139
00:12:41,666 --> 00:12:43,416
HAVEN'T YOU, RE-L?

140
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:46,166
NOW WE'RE GOING TO TRY THINGS
MY WAY FOR A CHANGE.

141
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:49,375
- WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

142
00:12:49,458 --> 00:12:51,125
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

143
00:12:51,208 --> 00:12:53,833
