- NO, IF YOU'RE IGGY,

145
00:13:00,291 --> 00:13:03,541
THEN IGGY IS DEAD.
- WHAT?

146
00:13:03,625 --> 00:13:05,666
- IGGY WOULD NEVER
TALK TO ME LIKE THAT.

147
00:13:05,750 --> 00:13:08,416
- DON'T BE STUPID.
MY VOCAL PATTERNS ARE

148
00:13:08,500 --> 00:13:11,041
