OF YOUR CUSTOMIZATIONS TO ME.

149
00:13:11,125 --> 00:13:13,333
- IT'S MORE THAN THAT.
ALL OF THIS.

150
00:13:13,416 --> 00:13:16,333
THE REAL IGGY WOULD NEVER
THINK OF DOING IT.

151
00:13:17,916 --> 00:13:20,333
IF THIS IS HOW THE COGITO VIRUS
CHANGED YOU,

152
00:13:20,416 --> 00:13:21,958
THEN YOU MIGHT AS WELL
BE DEAD.

153
00:13:22,041 --> 00:13:25,375
THE REAL IGGY WAS INFECTED
WITH THE VIRUS AND HE DIED.

154
00:13:25,458 --> 00:13:27,875
- SHUT UP!

155
00:13:31,333 --> 00:13:34,666
YOU ALWAYS WERE
A SELFISH BITCH, RE-L.

156
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:37,041
THIS IS NOT HOW IT WORKS
ANYMORE.

157
00:13:37,125 --> 00:13:39,041
YOU DON'T GET
TO WRITE ME OFF JUST

158
00:13:39,125 --> 00:13:41,041
BECAUSE I'VE GOTTEN COMPLICATED.

159
00:13:41,125 --> 00:13:45,791
IF I'M DEAD, THEN TELL ME
WHO'S BEEN BY YOUR SIDE

160
00:13:45,875 --> 00:13:47,875
EVER SINCE YOU LEFT ROMDEAU?

161
00:13:47,958 --> 00:13:49,875
- THAT WAS--

162
00:13:49,958 --> 00:13:52,250
- YOU'RE JUST AWFUL,
AREN'T YOU?

163
00:13:52,333 --> 00:13:55,375
YOU'RE SAYING THAT WASN'T ME?

164
00:13:55,458 --> 00:13:58,041
I WANT YOU TO TELL ME, RE-L,

165
00:13:58,125 --> 00:14:01,333
WHAT AM I?
I'M YOUR FAVORITE.

166
00:14:01,416 --> 00:14:03,416
YOU CUSTOMIZED ME
TO TALK THIS WAY.

167
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:04,708
- BASTARD.

168
00:14:04,791 --> 00:14:07,166
- OH, MY, WHAT A FACE
YOU'RE MAKING.

169
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:10,083
YOU KNOW YOU SHOULDN'T DO THAT.
YOU'LL GET WRINKLES.

170
00:14:10,166 --> 00:14:13,458
- YOU'RE A LIAR.  YOU'VE BEEN
LYING SINCE WE LEFT ROMDEAU.

171
00:14:13,541 --> 00:14:14,875
- LYING?

172
00:14:14,958 --> 00:14:16,541
- IT'S TOTALLY UNACCEPTABLE
FOR AN ENTOURAGE

173
00:14:16,625 --> 00:14:18,291
TO LIE TO ITS MASTER.

174
00:14:18,375 --> 00:14:21,208
THE LOYAL ENTOURAGE WOULD NEVER
BEHAVE THE WAY YOU'RE BEHAVING.

175
00:14:21,291 --> 00:14:24,250
YOU LIED TO ME,
TO YOUR MASTER.

176
00:14:24,333 --> 00:14:26,916
IGGY WOULD NEVER DO THAT.
IGGY IS DEAD.

177
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,791
- YOU'VE GOT TO BE KIDDING.

178
00:14:28,875 --> 00:14:31,333
WHO THE HELL DO YOU THINK'S
RESPONSIBLE FOR ALL THIS?

179
00:14:31,416 --> 00:14:34,000
SELFISH RE-L.
USELESS RE-L.

180
00:14:34,083 --> 00:14:35,708
INCOMPLETE RE-L.

181
00:14:35,791 --> 00:14:39,291
BESIDES ME, WHO COULD DEAL
WITH A WHINY BITCH LIKE YOU?

182
00:14:39,375 --> 00:14:40,833
- WHAT ARE YOU?

183
00:14:40,916 --> 00:14:43,666
