HOT-SHOT CAREER WOMAN

185
00:14:47,458 --> 00:14:49,541
ACROSS ROMDEAU.

186
00:14:49,625 --> 00:14:53,458
WHO REALLY MADE ALL
THAT POSSIBLE?

187
00:14:53,541 --> 00:14:57,333
WHO WAS THERE TO SUPPORT YOU,
YOU RECKLESS, ARROGANT BITCH?

188
00:14:57,416 --> 00:15:00,083
YOU SAY MY LIE WAS UNACCEPTABLE?

189
00:15:00,166 --> 00:15:02,958
IT'S YOUR LIE THAT'S
UNACCEPTABLE.

190
00:15:03,041 --> 00:15:06,833
SO STOP PRETENDING
YOU DON'T NEED ME.

191
00:15:06,916 --> 00:15:10,000
- WHAT ARE YOU PLANNING
TO DO TO ME?

192
00:15:10,083 --> 00:15:13,291
- ( laughs ) LITTLE LATE
TO START WORRYING ABOUT THAT.

193
00:15:13,375 --> 00:15:14,916
- TELL ME.

194
00:15:16,666 --> 00:15:18,541
- WHAT I ALWAYS DO.

195
00:15:18,625 --> 00:15:20,333
I'M GOING TO PROTECT YOU.
- ( gasps )

196
00:15:23,333 --> 00:15:26,333
- RE-L, YOU SAID THAT
AN AUTOREIV LIKE ME

197
00:15:26,416 --> 00:15:31,291
COULD NEVER TRULY UNDERSTAND YOU
BECAUSE I DON'T HAVE A SOUL.

198
00:15:31,375 --> 00:15:34,708
BUT I DO HAVE A SOUL.

199
00:15:34,791 --> 00:15:37,250
HOW DID YOU NOT NOTICE?

200
00:15:39,416 --> 00:15:42,833
WE CAN'T MAKE IT BACK
TO ROMDEAU IN THE U-4 ANYMORE.

201
00:15:42,916 --> 00:15:44,500
BUT THERE'S STILL THE SHIP.

202
00:15:44,583 --> 00:15:47,083
THAT WAS YOUR IDEA,
WASN'T IT?

203
00:15:47,166 --> 00:15:51,500
- AND WHAT HAPPENS AFTER
YOU STEAL THE SHIP?

204
00:15:51,583 --> 00:15:54,083
EVEN IF WE MAKE IT BACK,
YOU'RE STILL INFECTED.

205
00:15:54,166 --> 00:15:56,750
THEY'LL HAVE YOU DESTROYED.

206
00:16:21,625 --> 00:16:23,291
- ( gasps )

207
00:16:26,875 --> 00:16:29,750
- VINCE!
- PINO.

208
00:16:29,833 --> 00:16:33,208
- LOOK, I'M HELPING
BECAUSE I'M GOOD.  SEE?

209
00:16:33,291 --> 00:16:36,833
- VERY NICE.
NOW FIND THESE.

210
00:16:36,916 --> 00:16:39,791
- ROGER!

211
00:16:39,875 --> 00:16:42,833
HEY, VINCE, LIKE THIS?

212
00:16:42,916 --> 00:16:44,250
- YEAH.

213
00:16:45,708 --> 00:16:47,791
- THIS ONE?
- YEP.

214
00:16:47,875 --> 00:16:49,750
- ( humming )

215
00:16:57,083 --> 00:16:59,916
- ( gasps ) IT'S YOU.

216
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,583
- I'M NOT GOING TO HURT YOU.

217
00:17:03,166 --> 00:17:04,708
- PINO, THAT'S ENOUGH.

218
00:17:06,666 --> 00:17:09,583
I KNOW YOU.
YOU'RE RE-L'S--

219
00:17:15,166 --> 00:17:18,583
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
WITH HER GUN?

220
00:17:20,666 --> 00:17:22,375
WHERE'S RE-L?

221
00:17:22,458 --> 00:17:25,958
- RE-L'S GOING TO
KILL YOU SOMEDAY.

222
00:17:26,041 --> 00:17:29,583
SO WHY DO YOU NEED HER?

223
00:17:36,500 --> 00:17:39,000
- RE-L'S NOT SAFE WITH YOU.

224
00:17:40,583 --> 00:17:43,875
YOU'RE DESTINED
TO KILL HER.

225
00:17:43,958 --> 00:17:45,625
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

226
00:17:47,958 --> 00:17:51,625
- Iggy: I'VE SEEN IT.
A HIDEOUS MONSTER TORMENTING

227
00:17:51,708 --> 00:17:56,125
RE-L AS SHE LIES STRUGGLING
IN AGONY.

228
00:17:56,208 --> 00:17:59,625
YOU ARE THE MONSTER,
VINCENT LAW.

229
00:17:59,708 --> 00:18:02,958
- THIS IS INSANE.
WHY WOULD I KILL RE-L?

230
00:18:08,041 --> 00:18:10,125
- THAT FACE.

231
00:18:10,208 --> 00:18:12,291
IT'S THE SAME WAY YOU LOOKED
WHEN RE-L PULLED

232
00:18:12,375 --> 00:18:14,291
THIS GUN ON YOU.

233
